For purposes of this section, the term "state-administered retirement system" shall include:
The Kentucky Employees Retirement System, the County Employees Retirement System, and the State Police Retirement System administered by the Kentucky Retirement Systems and established under the provisions of KRS 16.505 to 16.652, 61.510 to 61.705, and 78.510 to 78.852;
The Kentucky Teachers' Retirement System established under KRS 161.220 to 161.716;
The Judicial Retirement Plan established under KRS 21.345 to 21.580; and
The Legislators' Retirement Plan established under KRS 6.500 to 6.577.
